data.description:
CUTENESS overload in this corner lot, brick home! This home features 2 beds/1bath on the main level with updated paint throughout and GORGEOUS HARDWOOD FLOORS! You are within walking distance to the parks and schools and less than a 5 minute drive to shopping and restaurants. This beauty is priced to sell and is ready for your personal touches! Included: refrigerator, electric oven and microwave. Basement is plumbed for a shower and toilet. Bonus fenced in area on side yard! There is a brand-new water heater in basement, roof in 2012, A/C in 2016.  HOME IS SOLD AS IS.  1 year Cinch Home Warranty included for the buyer/s! Call your favorite Agent today to schedule a private showing!
* Professional pics coming 9/7/23.
